{"tid":1913973,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求amd 高手, 3600+b450+g skill 問題","createTime":"2020-03-07T08:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T15:02:29.000Z","uid":129312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b38ee6bd51904fc0017dc2692078c57f4610e5bd","tid":1913973,"uid":129312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"小第岩岩砌左部新機,bios 係最新version, windows 都未裝<br />\n<br />\nAMD R5 3600 w/ stock cooler<br />\nG SKILL F4-3200C16D-32GTZN 16GB X2 KIT CL16-18-18-38 1.35V<br />\nMSI B450 Gaming Pro carbon AC<br />\nMSI RTX2070S 8GB TRIO X<br />\nSAMSUNG 970EVO PLUS 500GB NVME<br />\nFOCUS GX-750W GOLD<br />\n<br />\n砌好哂一著機, 有畫面, 但bios 認唔到keyboard &amp; mouse<br />\n熄機開機, 再開開下, 畫面都冇埋, 著debug vga 燈<br />\n<br />\n試插張用緊既舊gtx1060 6g, 都係著debug vga<br />\n<br />\n再張兩條ram 遂條試, 其中一條懷疑壤既著debug cpu, 一條就點都成功著機, a1-b2 4條ram 槽都冇問題, 冇問題既行2133 1.22V, 開左xmp 行3200, 1.36V<br />\n<br />\n試埋手上有兩條16G samsung 2666 ddr4 普通ram, 都著到機, 反而兩條samsung 16gb 2666 上到3200, 只係慢CL<br />\n<br />\n咁以為係其中一條g skill 壞, 點知插去第二部intel 係著到機入windows<br />\n<br />\n跟住返去amd 機, 咁又試下張條g skill 加到1.35V, 加NB/SOC V, 降到2133, 1866, reset cmos 後都係hold 住係bios, 都係同買返黎一樣, 認唔到keyboard &amp; mouse<br />\n<br />\n一路都幫人砌開intel, 起碼15年冇砌amd, 係咪amd 有新野玩, 我只求著機同有機會開xmp 姐, 仲要比friend 笑"},{"pid":"cfbfaa3f1755702521d8fab108106e8d65a4b69b","tid":1913973,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"check 下會唔會有新Bios version update?"},{"pid":"a892a6d2762c9052c8529efeb0bd5521736d58ac","tid":1913973,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:14:39.000Z","msg":"bios update 左未?"},{"pid":"25f6cf0246244280b9c055903ac77c39cbde35f7","tid":1913973,"uid":58882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:42:09.000Z","msg":"ram slot : a2 b2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 